title: J. Lawton Smith - Neuro Ophthalmology lectures - mp3
description:
This is an historical collection representing the work of a renown Neuro-Ophthalmologist from University of Miami, J Lawton Smith, MD. The material is dated. All lectures were originally delivered in the early to mid 1970's. Additionally, the views and opinions expressed in the lectures are those of J Lawton Smith and not those of the North American Neuro-Ophthalmology Society (NANOS).

The lectures are in MP3 audio format. An MP3 player is required to listen to them. Recommended players are: Windows Media Player and QuickTime.

Lectures may be viewed within the context of the NANOS curriculum, or in Dr. Smith's original outline.

A very well explained lecture series
